title: Bruhin Software - Community Sponsor of PyCon DE & PyData
---
full_description: Bruhin Software is a freelance company founded by Freya Bruhin and based in Winterthur, Switzerland. Freya Bruhin is actively involved in a range of open-source software projects while maintaining a pragmatic approach, always choosing the right tool for the job and the specific circumstances. Bruhin Software offers consulting, training, and development services. Freya Bruhin is an experienced software developer whose primary focus is on consulting and training in Python, including both fundamentals and advanced language features, in graphical user interface development with PyQt and PySide / Qt for Python, and in testing with pytest. With extensive expertise in Python, PyQt/PySide, and pytest, Freya Bruhin has worked across a wide variety of use cases and technical challenges involving these technologies. Bruhin Software supports clients in getting started, overcoming technical roadblocks, and applying established best practices.        website: https://bruhin.software

